author: Ikran Dahir
title: This Teen's TikTok Challenge Blew Up While Everyone Was On Coronavirus Lockdown
description: Kerrington Keyes created the challenge in February, but it really took off when people started to stay at home during the Coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Keyes said he was surprised to see it become so viral because when he had posted it initially it only got a few hundred views.
